ysis with real data. While the final\neBOSS Ly$\\alpha$ BAO analysis measured $D_M/D_H(z_\\mathrm{eff}=2.33)$ with\n$4\\%$ statistical precision, a full-shape fit of the same correlations could\nprovide a $\\sim2\\%$ measurement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2022 18:06:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
