dy forces alone). As a consequence,\nour potentials may lead to different predictions when applied to light and\nintermediate-mass nuclei in ab initio calculations and, potentially, help solve\nsome of the outstanding problems in microscopic nuclear structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 06:03:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 18:26:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
