 and low magnetic field associated\nwith the PWN in question, as caveats for the possible physical connection of\nthe pulsar as the origin of this high energy source.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 10:05:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
