,\nrespectively. Additionaly, a clear transition from ic-RL to mode tunable\ncoherent RL (c-RL) emission is also possible by altering the configuration of\nthe 2D-YP@RhB container. Therefore, the newly designed Van der Waals\nheterostructure, i.e., 2D-YP with intrinsic photon trapping capability may pave\nan avenue towards developing future exciting optoelectronic devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 10:34:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
