 for fast\nlocal inference.Besides, to prevent the loss of model capacity caused by\ncompression, we propose a bidirectional self-supervised knowledge distillation\nframework. Extensive experimental results on two benchmark datasets demonstrate\nthat compared with existing methods, the proposed on-device recommender not\nonly achieves an 8x inference speedup with a large compression ratio but also\nshows superior recommendation performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 14:23:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2022 09:49:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 04:57:03 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 12:25:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-09"}
